don't you, Cattermole?

53:47.140 --> 53:51.101
-Downstairs?
-To interrogate your wife.

53:51.978 --> 53:55.939
Now, if my wife's blood status
were in doubt...

53:56.107 --> 53:58.984
...and the head of the Department
of Magical Law Enforcement...

53:59.152 --> 54:04.740
...needed a job doing,
I think I might just make that a priority.

54:05.325 --> 54:07.492
You have one hour.

54:19.255 --> 54:24.927
Oh, my God. What am I gonna do?
My wife's all alone downstairs.

54:25.219 --> 54:29.514
-Ron, you don't have a wife.
-Oh, right.

54:29.682 --> 54:31.642
FEMALE VOlCE [OVER SPEAKERS]:
Level 2.

54:32.435 --> 54:34.561
RON:
But how do l stop it raining?

54:34.729 --> 54:37.356
HERMlONE:
Try "Finite Incantatem."

54:37.523 --> 54:39.358
FEMALE VOlCE:
Department of Magical Law Enforcement...

54:39.525 --> 54:40.984
...and Improper Use of Magic Department.

54:41.152 --> 54:43.111
HERMlONE:
This is you, Ron.

54:47.367 --> 54:52.204
Finite Incantatem. Okay.
And if that doesn't work...?

55:04.092 --> 55:07.052
FEMALE VOlCE: Level 1,
Minister of Magic and support staff.

55:07.220 --> 55:09.346
If we don't locate Umbridge
within the hour...

55:09.514 --> 55:11.515
...we go find Ron
and come back another day.

55:11.683 --> 55:12.724
-Deal?
-Yes.

55:16.270 --> 55:18.605
Ah, Mafalda. Travers sent you, did he?

55:18.773 --> 55:21.858
